> **NEVER create new documentation files — update existing SSOT docs.**
> **CHALLENGE before EXECUTE. Process before code.**
> **SEARCH before CREATE — verify no duplication exists.**

## ORCHESTRATION PROTOCOL (MANDATORY)

> **Every message follows:** INTAKE -> CHALLENGE -> PLAN -> GATE -> EXECUTE -> VERIFY -> LEARN
> **Canonical spec:** `egos-lab/.guarani/orchestration/`
> **Domain rules (local):** `.guarani/orchestration/DOMAIN_RULES.md`

| Complexity | Pipeline Depth | Min Thoughts |
|------------|---------------|---------------|
| TRIVIAL (typo, import) | Skip to Execute | 0 |
| SIMPLE (add field, fix bug) | Intake + Plan + Execute | 0 |
| MODERATE (component, API) | Full pipeline, questions mandatory | 3 |
| COMPLEX (feature, payment) | Full pipeline + Sequential Thinking | 5 |
| CRITICAL (migration, auth) | Full pipeline + user approval | 7 |

## MANDAMENTOS

1. **CHALLENGE** → Do NOT just accept user input. Question, detect contradictions
2. **READ** → "Já Concluído" = NÃO REIMPLEMENTAR
3. **THINK** → Sequential Thinking para tasks P0/P1 (min 5 thoughts)
4. **COMMIT** → Convencional (feat:/fix:/chore:) cada 30-60min
5. **SIZE** → Python: 400 lines/module, React: 500/component, 300/API route
6. **REUSE** → Verificar existente antes de criar novo
7. **VERIFY** → Python: `uv run ruff check src/` + `uv run pytest -x`. Frontend: `npx tsc --noEmit`
8. **TASKS** → Atualizar TASKS.md IMEDIATAMENTE após implementar feature
9. **ASK** → PERGUNTAR antes de criar páginas/features/campos novos
10. **SCOPE** → Fazer APENAS o que foi pedido, nada mais
11. **COST** → VPS $36/mês. Cada docker build = tempo. Commit often, deploy once.
12. **SEARCH** → Antes de criar arquivo, pesquisar se já existe equivalente

