## TEST DISCIPLINE (AI-Era)

| Priority | Type | When |
|----------|------|------|
| 1 | `ruff check` + `tsc --noEmit` | Before commit |
| 2 | `pytest -x --tb=short` | After changing API code |
| 3 | Integration against real Neo4j | After changing graph queries |
| 4 | E2E manual test on VPS | Before announcing changes |

```
❌ No new unit tests with mocks
